{"tid":986393,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中廣核擬英國建核電廠 填補日立東芝空缺","createTime":"2019-01-18T11:41:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-19T04:22:59.000Z","uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"edbc9bd01bf33a76ee2b0bf30e40c9a69f22b357","tid":986393,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T11:41:09.000Z","msg":"中國廣核集團表示，將提出在英國建設一座核電廠的計劃，以填補兩個日本項目失敗留下的空缺。<br />\n<br />\n英國一直希望能夠興建多座核電廠，以取代計劃在2020年代關閉的老舊煤炭和核電廠。不過，日立製作所稍早前證實，已凍結在英國威爾斯興建核電廠的計劃，東芝亦於去年取消英國NuGen核電項目。<br />\n<br />\n英國政府透露，在日立要求英國政府提供更多幫助後，已向其提出一套財務支持方案，但該公司認為該項目從經濟上來看仍不划算。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/china/article/2041543/%E4%B8%AD%E5%BB%A3%E6%A0%B8%E6%93%AC%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E5%BB%BA%E6%A0%B8%E9%9B%BB%E5%BB%A0+%E5%A1%AB%E8%A3%9C%E6%97%A5%E7%AB%8B%E6%9D%B1%E8%8A%9D%E7%A9%BA%E7%BC%BA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fchina%2Farticle%2F2041543%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25BB%25A3%25E6%25A0%25B8%25E6%2593%25AC%25E8%258B%25B1%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E6%25A0%25B8%25E9%259B%25BB%25E5%25BB%25A0%2B%25E5%25A1%25AB%25E8%25A3%259C%25E6%2597%25A5%25E7%25AB%258B%25E6%259D%25B1%25E8%258A%259D%25E7%25A9%25BA%25E7%25BC%25BA&d=xP31a004xBweYVfCBK2M7mi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=e0e71a22\" target=\"_blank\">http://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/china/article/2041543/%E4%B8%AD%E5%BB%A3%E6%A0%B8%E6%93%AC%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E5%BB%BA%E6%A0%B8%E9%9B%BB%E5%BB%A0+%E5%A1%AB%E8%A3%9C%E6%97%A5%E7%AB%8B%E6%9D%B1%E8%8A%9D%E7%A9%BA%E7%BC%BA</a>"},{"pid":"8d9fd7135e0e751a0c525a1d9c99d13527a58a8f","tid":986393,"uid":60366,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T11:43:50.000Z","msg":"人地批你先算"},{"pid":"8c2c21fa86214dfd6b00cf8d333141054c1bd4e5","tid":986393,"uid":165782,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T11:45:54.000Z","msg":"如果係真嘅 英國再唔值得人崇拜"},{"pid":"0f0eb2e7d7f2f0cd260cc510d2775a693498a05b","tid":986393,"uid":213877,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":